'''巴哥犬'''（{{lang-en|Pug}}）, 原中文名'''[[哈巴狗|哈巴狗]]'''，又稱作'''巴哥'''。是一種小型觀賞[[犬|犬]]，巴哥犬面黑，有很多褶皺，成年時身高大約25到28厘米，體重約為5至13[[公斤|公斤]]，壽命大約為12到15年。個性溫和。巴哥犬是優秀的家庭犬（house dog），在室內時不喜吠叫，警戒時低沉、響亮的吠叫聲，又足以使門外的陌生人誤以為是大型犬，而有警示的作用<ref name="#1"> {{Cite book | author = Wilhelmina Swainston-Goodger | title = The Pug-Dog - Its History and Origin | location = 英國 | publisher = Read Country Books | date = 2005 | language = en }} </ref>。

== 簡介 ==
原產地：中國[[西藏|西藏]]<ref name="AKC History">{{cite web| url=http://www.akc.org/breeds/pug/history.cfm| title=American Kennel Club - Pug History| work=AKC.org| location=| publisher=American Kennel Club| accessdate=2006-08-19| archive-date=2015-02-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150204082901/http://www.akc.org/breeds/pug/history.cfm| dead-url=no}}</ref>

毛色：銀灰色、紅黃色、淺黃褐色、黑色（在19世紀末期始出現<ref name="#1"/>） 

毛質：柔軟而有光澤，觸感滑順

個性：溫馴、聰明、忠誠、友善、體貼、安靜、有耐心、愛乾淨、自尊心強、愛撒嬌、和蔼可親、愛家、啟爆

[[File:Cute_PUG_6_years_old.jpg|缩略图]]

== 名称起源 ==
{{OR|哈巴的意思為走路時兩膝向外彎曲。<ref>清 [[張杰鑫|張杰鑫]]《[[三俠劍|三俠劍]]》第一回：「他哈巴著羅圈腿，假意的走歪斜啦，來至柵欄切近。」</ref>}}

外表富有魅力，18世纪末正式命名为“巴哥”（Pug），「pug」 一詞來自[[古英語|古英語]] pugg，這是一個小朋友的好玩的親切術語。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=4ZkRAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA376&lpg=PA376&dq=pug+pugnus+pugg&source=web&ots=_uV8_Im2f5&sig=LkgomiwC4_iCbnHQmQKLrLkK8GI&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=pug%20pugnus%20pugg&f=false |title=存档副本 |access-date=2019-10-12 |archive-date=2021-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313200421/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=4ZkRAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA376&lpg=PA376&dq=pug+pugnus+pugg&source=web&ots=_uV8_Im2f5&sig=LkgomiwC4_iCbnHQmQKLrLkK8GI&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=pug%20pugnus%20pugg&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>或古英語pūca，意思是goblin、demon。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/pug |title=存档副本 |access-date=2019-10-12 |archive-date=2021-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313200425/https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/pug |dead-url=no }}</ref>
哈巴狗幼犬被稱為pugletitos。<ref>Shipley, Joseph Twadell (1955). Dictionary of Early English. New York, EE.UU.: Philosophical Library. pp. 768 pages.</ref>

== 體型特徵 ==
巴哥犬身體比例勻稱結實，比例勻稱呈方形，頭大黑臉黑鼻子，額頭有皺紋，小小的垂耳，臉部極具特徵，日耳曼系國家稱之為'''墨普斯犬'''（皺起來的臉）。胸腹肌肉健壯，四肢短小，緊緊捲曲的尾巴，是溫馴的狗，很喜歡和人相處且對環境的適應力極佳。

== 起源與歷史 ==
巴哥犬源於中國，有些人認為巴哥犬的祖先為北京犬，另外有些人看巴哥就好像縮小比例的獒犬。巴哥犬源於西藏培育，17世紀時由荷蘭傳到歐洲，當時在英國即把牠稱為「荷蘭犬」，據說飼養相當普遍，而目前的品種是後來在英國培育改良而成的。

== 健康問題與品種改良的關聯 ==
巴哥犬，與[[法國鬥牛犬|法國鬥牛犬]]、[[北京犬|北京犬]]、[[西施犬|西施犬]]同樣屬於扁平臉（flat-faced）或稱短頭（brachycephalic）的犬種，這樣的特徵使得巴哥犬容易有許多健康問題，包含：呼吸系統、眼疾、脊椎疾病、心臟病與肺炎。與一般犬種的平均壽命相比，巴哥犬的平均壽命會減少四歲。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2020/08/200826140905.htm |title=Why flat-faced dogs remain popular despite health problems |author=PLOS |date=2020-08-26|publisher=Science Daily |language=en |accessdate=2021-01-25|quote= But these breeds are strongly predisposed to a range of severe disorders, including respiratory disease, eye disease, spinal disease, heat stroke and pneumonia, and their lifespan is reduced by on average four years compared to dogs with longer muzzles. }}</ref> 因為這些健康問題，有獸醫呼籲應謹慎考慮購買巴哥犬<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.sciencefocus.com/news/stop-and-think-before-buying-a-flat-faced-dog-the-royal-veterinary-college-warns/|title=Stop and think before buying a flat-faced dog, the Royal Veterinary College warns |author= Jason Goodyer |date=2020-10-14 |publisher=Science Focus |language=en |accessdate=2021-01-25|quote= “Stop and think before buying a flat-faced dog”. }}</ref>；英國獸醫協會亦呼籲商人應停止在情人節賀卡上印製巴哥犬的肖像，因為這樣的商業化往往激起消費者對於扁平臉犬種的狂熱，卻忽略這些犬種的福祉。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5379291/Push-pugs-Valentines-cards-says-vets.html |title=Push the pugs off Valentine’s cards says vets who worry their faces on merchandise is fuelling a craze for flat-faced pets despite concerns over their welfare |author=MILES DILWORTH FOR MAILONLINE |date=2018-02-11 |publisher=Daily Mail |language=en |accessdate=2021-01-25 |quote=The British Veterinary Association say their prominence on merchandise is fuelling a craze for flat-faced pets despite concerns over their welfare. |archive-date=2021-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313200426/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5379291/Push-pugs-Valentines-cards-says-vets.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

作為古老的犬種，巴哥犬如今的扁平臉特徵，是二十世紀之後犬業[[人工選擇|人工選擇]]的結果<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-3480780/How-humans-changed-man-s-best-friend-pictures-100-years-breeding-changed-dog-breeds-not-better.html |title=How man has changed his best friend: How 100 years of intensive breeding has left some dog breeds unrecognisable - and in pain |author=https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-3480780/How-humans-changed-man-s-best-friend-pictures-100-years-breeding-changed-dog-breeds-not-better.html |date=2016-03-08 |publisher=Daily Mail |language=en |accessdate=2021-01-25 |8= |archive-date=2021-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313203133/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-3480780/How-humans-changed-man-s-best-friend-pictures-100-years-breeding-changed-dog-breeds-not-better.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。為了符合民眾對於寬大、扁平臉特徵的偏好（這樣的偏好則來自人類對於「似幼童的」特徵的喜愛<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2020/aug/11/pets-how-we-hurt-the-animals-we-cherish |title=Love you to death: how we hurt the animals we cherish |author=Esther Woolfson |date=2020-08-11 |publisher=The Guardian |language=en |accessdate=2021-01-25 |quote=One suggestion is that the “childlike” appearance of dogs such as pugs and bulldogs attracts us |archive-date=2021-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315152714/https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2020/aug/11/pets-how-we-hurt-the-animals-we-cherish |dead-url=no }}</ref>），犬業縮短了巴哥犬的頭顱並拓寬其口腔頂，以強化扁平臉的特徵。相比十八世紀英國著名繪家[[威廉·賀加斯|威廉·賀加斯]]在其作品《威廉·賀加斯自畫像》（Painter and his Pug）所描繪的巴哥犬形象中，仍有明顯的吻部；如今[[美國犬業俱樂部|美國犬業俱樂部]]所認可的巴哥犬種吻部標準則是：短、鈍、成方形<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.akc.org/dog-breeds/pug/ |title=Pug |author=American Kennel Club |publisher=American Kennel Club |language=en |accessdate=2021-01-25 |quote=The muzzle is short, blunt, square, but not upfaced. |archive-date=2021-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313200309/https://www.akc.org/dog-breeds/pug/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[中國|中國]]更有不道德的犬業培育出「鷹版巴哥」，增加巴哥犬鼻子上的皺褶，加劇呼吸困難的健康問題。

近年有獸醫呼籲道德培育（Ethical breeding）與「復古」巴哥犬，使巴哥犬的特徵回到過去，透過不過分強調扁平臉特徵，得以在保留巴哥犬特徵的同時，培育出更健康的犬種。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cbc.ca/cbcdocspov/features/by-picking-pug-dogs-for-their-cute-factor-were-creating-health-problems-say |title=By picking pug dogs for their cute factor, we’re creating health problems, say experts |author=Nina Dragicevic |publisher=CBC News |language=en |accessdate=2021-01-25 |quote=Arthur says a healthier pug is possible — breeding for “less exaggerated” traits means we might be able to keep the pug but reduce the health problems. |archive-date=2021-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313200523/https://www.cbc.ca/cbcdocspov/features/by-picking-pug-dogs-for-their-cute-factor-were-creating-health-problems-say |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 飼養要領 ==
要留意勿傷及其突出的眼睛；皺摺與皺摺之間要勤於擦拭，耳朵內部及皺皮中也別忘了清理。此外，因為不適應高溫多濕的環境，其皮膚與耳朵需格外留心，尤其在夏季時必須做好空調管理；易發胖，需控制飲食並有充足的運動量。

巴哥犬其實很需要主人陪伴牠、注意牠，其實牠是忠誠、像孩子般的狗，喜歡別人拍拍哄哄，別因為外貌而對牠心生誤解，其實牠很需要主人關愛的。

